Bryant's store to the left is like a body of water.

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:11.000
I can remember when I like seven years old we lived there.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:18.000
And this, I forgot what we called it, it was just overflow and our houses on the other side of the road.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:22.000
And water would run under the house all night, watch the bridges out.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:25.000
And you couldn't, it was fun to us, you know, sell this water.

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:29.000
Clear water, you could see fish is going, but it wouldn't build up because it was going back

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:31.000
